<div class="flex flex-col justify-center sm:px-2 lg:px-2">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl border-2 border-primary-500 p-3">
    <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Helping Central Texas
    </h2>
     <p class="mt-8 text-left text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Winter Storm Shirley has caused massive suffering in the state of Texas. As of this writing, many
      Texans are still without power, running water, potable water, medicine, transportation, and shelter. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-left text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      This site was crated to provide a simple platform for those with resources to connect with those in need.
      If you have even just a few spare bottles of water or blankets, please post here and you will be paired with
      people in need.   
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-left text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      We are hopig to be able to facilitate resource sharing throughout the central Texas metropolitan areas. 
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-left text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Helping Central Texas is simply a platform to consolidate aid. Adapted from the open-source 
      <%= link_to 'Help With Covid', 'http://www.helpwithcovid.com', class: "text-blue-500 font-bold hover:text-blue-300", target: "_blank" %>
       platform, with help from <%= link_to 'ResiTown Sacramento', 'http://www.resitown.com', class: "text-blue-500 font-bold hover:text-blue-300", target: "_blank" %>
        and <%= link_to 'City Help', 'http://www.city-help.org', class: "text-blue-500 font-bold hover:text-blue-300", target: "_blank" %>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl">
    <a id='how-it-works'>
      <h2 class="mt-6 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
        How Does It Work?
      </h2>
    </a>
     <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      Helping Central Texas is a web-based platform, where youâ€™ll be able to sign-up for local aid or provide it if you need it. 
    </p>
    <h3 class="mt-6 text-center text-2xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
    Here are step-by-step instructions:
    </h3>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
    <p class="mt-8 text-center text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600 max-w">
      <ol id="instructions" class="mt-4 list-none pl-15 text-sm leading-5 text-gray-600">
        <li>1. Create a profile on the HCT website or click <%= link_to 'here', new_user_registration_path, target: "_blank", class: "font-bold text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-300" %></li>
        <li>2. Find a resource you need, or post a resource you have</li>
        <li>3. Sign-up for the resource if you are in need</li>
        <li>4. Sit tight and an email with additional details will be sent to your inbox</li>
      </ol>  
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div align="center" class="flex flex-col mt-8">
    <div class="sm:-mx-6 sm:px-6 lg:-mx-8 lg:px-8">
      <div class="align-middle inline-block w-max shadow overflow-hidden sm:rounded-lg border-b border-gray-200">
        <table id="team-table" class="w-max table-fixed">
          <tbody>
          <% striped_classes_cycle = [ "bg-white", "bg-gray-50" ] %>
          <% TEAM.each do |group, team| %>
            <% if !group.empty? %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td colspan="3" class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm leading-5 font-medium text-white text-center bg-primary-500">
                  <%= html_escape group %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
            <% team.each do |name, role, desc| %>
              <tr class="<%= cycle striped_classes_cycle %>">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap text-sm w-1/3 leading-5 font-medium text-gray-900 text-left">
                  <%= html_escape name %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap w-1/3 text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-right">
                  <%= html_escape role %>
                </td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-no-wrap w-1/3 text-sm leading-5 text-gray-500 text-left">
                  <%= desc %>
                </td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full w-screen">
    <h3 class="mt-8 text-center text-xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
    This platform is powered by City Help!
    </h3>
    <div class="mt-8 text-center w-max items-center text-xl text-primary-400 leading-9">
      <ul id="city-help-links" class="text-center items-center font-bold">
        <li class="mr-10 inline hover:text-primary-300">
          <%= link_to "Athens Help With Covid", "http://athenshelpwithcovid.com", target: "_blank" %>
        </li>
        <li class="mr-10 inline hover:text-primary-300">
        <%= link_to "New Haven Help With Covid", "https://newhavenhelpwithcovid.com", target: "_blank" %>
        </li>
        <li class="mr-10 inline hover:text-primary-300">
        <%= link_to "City Help", "https://city-help.org/", target: "_blank" %>
        </li>
        <li class="mr-10 inline hover:text-primary-300">
        <%= link_to "ResiTown Sacramento", "https://resitown.com/", target: "_blank" %>
        </li>
        <li class="mr-10 inline hover:text-primary-300">
        <%= link_to "Help With Covid", "https://helpwithcovid.com/", target: "_blank" %>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-lg">
    <h2 class="mt-8 text-center text-3xl leading-9 font-extrabold text-gray-900">
      Thank you to all volunteers!
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>

